==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea god
<hw>Sea" god`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A marine deity; a fabulous being
supposed to live in, or have dominion over, the sea, or some particular
sea or part of the sea, as Neptune.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sea goddess</ent>⟦br⟧
